{"id":10849,"type":6,"name":"Life on Mars (US)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3c/2e/10849_EQr4Z.jpg","summary":"　　美版火星生活的主创者是David E. Kelley（\"Boston Legal\"）。拍摄已于8月14号开始，计划mid-season在ABC播出。在经过“一番令人疲惫的寻找”以后，男主角Sam Tyler已经确定由爱尔兰演员Jason O'Mara扮演。Gene Hunt则由另一位爱尔兰演员Colm Meaney扮演。O'Mara曾经为ABC拍摄过Marlowe（硬汉派侦探小说家钱德勒笔下的私家侦探Marlowe）的首集。Meaney曾经主演过Star Trek: Deep Space 9，并且在爱尔兰电影Intermission等影片中扮演过警长。女主角Annie Cartwright由制服女警改为正式的探员，由Rachelle Lefevre扮演，她是几个主演中最早确定下来的人选。Sam在2006年的女友Maya由印度裔改为华裔。首集由Thomas Schlamme执导，剧本由Kelley执笔，首集的主要情节保持英版原状不变。Schlamme说，“我读剧本的时候，觉得坏消息是主角必须能同时演出自信和迷茫，强硬和惊恐，孤僻和亲善，永不妥协却又不乏喜剧色彩，好消息是我们有了Jason O'Mara”。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>火星生活美版 第一季</li><li><span>集数: </span>17</li><li><span>开始: </span>2008-10-09</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 悬疑 / 犯罪</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>ABC</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0787490</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"doing":2},"eps":[{"id":64398,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64398","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64399,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64399","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64400,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64400","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64401,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64401","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64402,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64402","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64403,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64403","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":64404,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/64404","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"i